<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>CMBS Offerings</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@materializecss/materialize@2.2.1/dist/css/materialize.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/main.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@materializecss/materialize@2.2.1/dist/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="/static/visulate-tiny.png" type="image/png">

  </head>
  <body>

    {{!-- Navigation Bar --}}
    <nav class="navbar blue darken-4">
      <div class="nav-wrapper">
        <a href="#" class="brand-logo" style="padding-left: 8px;">Visulate CMBS</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    {{!-- Main Content --}}
    <div class="container">

      {{!-- Introduction Card --}}
      <div class="row" style="margin-top: 15px;">
        <div class="col s12">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-content">
              <span class="card-title">Welcome to Visulate CMBS</span>
              <p>This application provides access to Commercial Mortgage-Backed Securities (CMBS) data. You can use it to explore property-level details for loans that collateralize a CMBS trust. </p>
              <br/>
              <p>CMBS are a type of asset-backed security that pools together mortgages on commercial properties, such as office buildings, shopping centers, and hotels. Investors in CMBS receive regular payments based on the cash flows generated by the underlying mortgages. CMBS data is reported to the SEC under Regulation AB II, which requires issuers to provide detailed information about the underlying assets in a standardized format. This data is submitted using SEC Form <a href="/cmbs/ABS-EE">ABS-EE</a>. Issuing entities also submit deal-specific information using a <a href="/cmbs/FWP">FWP</a>.</p>
              <br/>
              <p>Visulate CMBS is designed to help you explore this data in a user-friendly way. You can view property details, ask follow-up questions, and get insights into the underlying assets of CMBS offerings. Start by selecting a CMBS offering from the dropdown list below. Once selected, you can view property details and ask follow-up questions.</p>
              <br/>
              <p>If you have any questions or feedback, please contact <a href="mailto:support@visulate.com">support@visulate.com</a> or contact Susan Goldthorp on (321) 698 5198</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{!-- CMBS Offering selection --}}
      <div class="row" style="margin-top: 15px;">
        <div class="col s12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="input-field col s12">
              <i class="material-icons prefix">corporate_fare</i>
              <input type="text" id="autocomplete-input" class="autocomplete">
              <label for="autocomplete-input">Select a CMBS Offering</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        {{!-- <div class="col s12">
          <ul class="tabs">
            <li class="tab col s3"><a class="active"href="#properties">Properties</a></li>
            <li class="tab col s3"><a href="#offering">Offering Details</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div> --}}
        <div class="col s12" id="properties"></div>
        <div class="col s12" id="offering"></div>  {{!-- Full width on small screens --}}
      </div>


    {{!-- display a working dialog during long running operations --}}
      <div class="row" >
        <div class="col s12 m8 offset-m2" id="working-dialog" style="display: none;"> {{!-- Full width on small screens, 8 columns on medium and up --}}
          <div class="card-panel ">
            <span id="working-message">Working...
            </span>
            <div class="progress"> <div class="indeterminate"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{!-- Follow-up questions --}}
      <div class="row" id="follow-up-questions" style="display: none;">
        <div class="col s12 m10 offset-m1">
          <form class="col s12" id="chat-form">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="input-field col s12">
                <textarea id="chat-input" class="materialize-textarea" placeholder=" "></textarea>
                <label for="chat-input">Follow-up Questions</label>
              <a id="chat-submit-fab" class="btn-floating btn-small waves-effect waves-light blue"><i class="material-icons">send</i></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>  {{!-- container --}}
    <script>
      window.MAPS_API_KEY = "{{MAPS_API_KEY}}";
      window.trusts = {{{json trusts}}};
    </script>
    <script type="module" src="/static/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>